++	 * The gpiolib-cdev, gpiolib-sysfs and gpio-keys input driver all call
++	 * the gpiochip's .get() method after an edge event on a requested GPIO
++	 * occurs.
++	 *
++	 * We ensure that the .get() method reads 1 for the button GPIO for some
++	 * time.
++	 */
